OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778220038
OL,3,CCalocane charge 'more understandable
OL,4,Cas second degree murder', inquiry hears
OL,6,FTim Moloney KC, who represents the
OL,7,Ffamilies of Mr Webber, Ms O'Malley-
OL,8,FKumar and Mr Coates, asked Mr Rogers
OL,9,Fon Wednesday if he had felt concerned
OL,10,Fabout the "relationship between the
OL,11,Ffamilies and the CPS" during the
OL,12,Fcourse of the investigation and
OL,13,Fprosecution of Calocane.
OL,15,FMr Rogers replied: "It was clear that
OL,16,Fthe CPS had tried their best to
OL,17,Fengage, inform, console, speak to
OL,18,Ffamilies throughout, and it was quite
OL,19,Fobvious, as part of this inspection,
OL,20,Fthat there were different expectations
OL,21,Fand understanding of a lot of issues."
OL,26,@rD@KOUsD@UO]wD@TOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778220038
OL,3,CCalocane charge 'more understandable
OL,4,Cas second degree murder', inquiry hears
OL,6,FA second degree murder charge would
OL,7,Frefer to a killing where the offender
OL,8,Fintended to do serious injury and was
OL,9,Faware of a serious risk of causing
OL,10,Fdeath, according to the 2024 HMCPSI
OL,11,Freport.
OL,13,FA second degree murder conviction
OL,14,Fwould also attract a discretionary
OL,15,Flife sentence.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
