CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778220038
OL,3,CCalocane charge 'more understandable
OL,4,Cas second degree murder', inquiry hears
OL,6,FThe inquiry also heard on Wednesday
OL,7,Fafternoon from Dr Tuhina Lloyd, who
OL,8,Fwas Calocane's community consultant at
OL,9,Fthe Nottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,10,FFoundation Trust's Early Intervention
OL,11,Fin Psychosis (EIP) service.
OL,13,FShe told the inquiry that her team had
OL,14,Fcome to feel "completely redundant"
OL,15,Fwhen the decision was taken in
OL,16,FSeptember 2022 to discharge Calocane
OL,17,Ffrom the mental health service to the
OL,18,FGP.
OL,26,@vD@NOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778220038
OL,3,CCalocane charge 'more understandable
OL,4,Cas second degree murder', inquiry hears
OL,6,F"We had tried over a nine-month period
OL,7,Fto engage VC (Valdo Calocane), and we
OL,8,Fhad failed," she said.
OL,10,FShe described how Calocane missed
OL,11,Faround nine appointments with her and
OL,12,Fhad told the inpatient team he felt
OL,13,F"persecuted" by the EIP service ` but
OL,14,Fshe could not trigger an assessment
OL,15,Funder the Mental Health Act because he
OL,16,Fstill did not meet the threshold for
OL,17,Fit.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]uD@AOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778220038
OL,3,CCalocane charge 'more understandable
OL,4,Cas second degree murder', inquiry hears
OL,6,F"We had absolutely no powers to get
OL,7,Fhim to come to appointments, we have
OL,8,Fno powers to get him to take his
OL,9,Ftreatment," Dr Lloyd said.
OL,11,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
